These are Puzzles for 2x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: mango, papaya, eggplant
The people have 3 different jobs:  paramedic, analyst, scientist
1. the person eating mango is in an even position##4
2. the paramedic is on the left or right of the scientist##3
3. the paramedic is the person eating papaya##1
4. the person eating eggplant is on the far left##1
5. the analyst is the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Food   | eggplant | mango | papaya |
| Job    | analyst    | scientist | paramedic |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-2::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, card-games, baking
The people use 3 different means of transport: bus, subway, train
1. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the far right##1
2. the person driving the subway is in an even position##4
3. the person driving the train is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
4. the person driving the subway is the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |     2      |      3      |
| Hobby       | card-games | baking | rock-climbing |
| Transport   | train    | subway     | bus        |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-3::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, dancing, woodworking
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, classical, soul
1. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
2. the fan of classical is on the left of the fan of gospel##1
3. the person who's hobby is dancing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |   3    |
| Hobby         | woodworking     | dancing | chess |
| Music-Genre   | classical | gospel     | soul  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-4::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: epic, western, thriller
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rowing, weightlifting, water-polo
1. the person watching western movies is the person who's sport is weightlifting##1
2. the person watching epic movies is the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person watching western movies is in an even position##4
4. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person watching thriller movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |    3     |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | western  | epic  |
| Sport         | rowing  | weightlifting | water-polo |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, fishing, board-games
There are 3 different nationalities: argentine, chinese, italian
1. the person who's hobby is board-games is between the person who's hobby is singing and the argentine##2
2. the person who's hobby is fishing is in an odd position##4
3. the italian is on the left of the argentine##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |    3     |
| Hobby         | singing   | board-games | fishing    |
| Nationality   | chinese | italian     | argentine |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-6::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: singing, board-games, rock-climbing
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: biathlon, soccer, volleyball
1. the person who's hobby is singing is the person who's sport is soccer##1
2. the person who's sport is volleyball is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
3. the person who's hobby is board-games is in an odd position##4
4. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby   | board-games | rock-climbing | singing   |
| Sport   | volleyball     | biathlon    | soccer |

