.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-7::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: family, epic, animation
3 different pets are kept: horse, frog, goldfish
1. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person watching family movies##1
2. the person watching family movies is between the owner of the goldfish and the person watching animation movies##2
3. the person watching family movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
4. the owner of the horse is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |   3    |
| Movie-Genre   | animation | family | epic |
| Pet           | frog         | horse         | goldfish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-8::.
There 3 different types of food: cherry, blueberry, spinach
3 different pets are kept: turtle, ferret, cat
1. the owner of the turtle is between the owner of the ferret and the person eating cherry##2
2. the owner of the cat is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the ferret is on the left of the person eating spinach##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |  2   |     3     |
| Food   | blueberry | spinach | cherry |
| Pet    | ferret    | turtle | cat     |

