.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-9::.
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: punk, metal, classical
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: skateboarding, weightlifting, badminton
1. the person who's sport is badminton is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the fan of punk##1
3. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the fan of metal##1
4. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left or right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2     |    3     |
| Music-Genre   | classical   | metal  | punk  |
| Sport         | badminton | weightlifting | skateboarding |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-10::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, mirinda, almond-milk
There 3 different types of food: raspberry, pepper, eggplant
1. the person eating raspberry is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
2. the person eating eggplant is in an even position##4
3. the person eating eggplant is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1    |     2     |   3    |
| Beverage   | hot-chocolate    | almond-milk      | mirinda |
| Food       | pepper | eggplant | raspberry   |

