2. the person driving the quad-bike is the security-guard##1
3. the person driving the train is the police-officer##1
4. the police-officer is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |    2    |     3      |
| Job         | bartender | police-officer | security-guard |
| Transport   | jet-ski | train   | quad-bike |

