.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-14::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: traveling, video-games, cooking
3 different pets are kept: rat, goat, guinea-pig
1. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person who's hobby is video-games and the owner of the goat##2
2. the person who's hobby is video-games is in an odd position##4
3. the owner of the goat is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person who's hobby is cooking is on the right of the owner of the rat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |   3    |
| Hobby   | video-games | cooking | traveling |
| Pet     | rat    | guinea-pig  | goat   |

