.:: Puzzle 2x3-Level-4-15::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: musical, martial-arts, action
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: house, dubstep, indie
1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching musical movies##1
2. the fan of dubstep is on the left of the fan of house##1
3. the fan of dubstep is on the left or right of the person watching action movies##3
4. the person watching action movies is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3    |
| Movie-Genre   | musical  | action     | martial-arts |
| Music-Genre   | dubstep | house | indie    |

