The people prefer 3 different music-genres: disco, ambient, pop
1. the fan of pop is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
2. the person who's hobby is writing is in the middle##1
3. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the fan of ambient##1
4. the fan of disco is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3     |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | writing   | board-games |
| Music-Genre   | ambient   | disco | pop      |

