There are 3 different nationalities: japanese, colombian, turkish
1. the turkish is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the person drinking fanta is in an odd position##4
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
4. the person drinking coffee is on the left of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2       |    3     |
| Beverage      | fanta | coffee | iced-tea |
| Nationality   | colombian   | turkish          | japanese |

